Annotation Interface AutowiredQualifier

@Target(FIELD) @Retention(RUNTIME) @Documented public @interface AutowiredQualifier
Using AutowiredQualifier annotation with Autowired or AutowiredAcceptNull annotation.

This annotation can be used to avoid conflict if there are multiple implementations of a same interface.
